    "Instruction tuning in pre-training also emerges as a significant factor (Yue et al., 2023).",
    "Model Scale.",
    "There's a noted correlation between parameter count and arithmetic capability in LLMs (Yuan et al., 2023).",
    "Larger models generally perform better, but a performance plateau is observed, as shown by Galactica's similar outcomes at 30B and 120B parameters.",
